    "stem": "A 78-year-old man with moderate Alzheimer's disease (MoCA 14/30) is currently taking donepezil 10 mg daily. His family reports his confusion has progressed significantly over the past year despite donepezil therapy. He now requires help with bathing and dressing. What medication should be added to his current regimen at this stage of his disease?",
