    "stem": "A 78-year-old man is admitted to the hospital for a hip fracture repair. On postoperative day 2, nurses report he is confused, agitated, hallucinating, and unable to recognize his wife — behaviors that were not present before surgery. His baseline cognitive function per family was intact. Which feature MOST distinguishes delirium from dementia?",
