    "stem": "A 68-year-old woman with a history of autoimmune thyroid disease presents with fatigue and difficulty with balance. Labs reveal HGB 10.2 g/dL with MCV 108 fL and serum B12 level of 112 pg/mL. She has no dietary restrictions. Which of the following is the most appropriate next step to confirm the diagnosis?",
